com.seagullsw.appinterface.client

Interface AppInterfaceConnectionBuilder


  • public interface AppInterfaceConnectionBuilder
    Specifies various manners of building AppInterfaceConnections. Each protocol package/class should implement a factory class that implements this interface.

    • Method Summary

      Builds a new AppInterfaceConnection based on the contents of the file at the URL.
